 咁呢3個地方就會自古以來就不是中國領土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"台灣要等到康熙時期先由中原王朝統治，都叫自古以來係中國領土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b533fae6df9ad839c7c3b542cba7b9bdd7073f4","tid":2343851,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e2472bacb3ad48dd41cca6bae946df39254b73","tid":2343851,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2f3ca6a66b9b2b469012124ec9b2d03f61371d5f","tid":2343851,"uid":274772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"香港自古以嚟係中國領土 個古係咩時間?係秦朝嘛<br />\n<br />\n但西藏 新疆 內蒙古當時未入中國版圖 按同一時段邏輯咁講 咁呢3個地方就會自古以來就不是中國領土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"台灣要等到康熙時期先由中原王朝統治，都叫自古以來係中國領土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"仲有中國大興安嶺以北於清朝都係中國領土 如果用台灣係清朝屬中國領土 咁今日淪陷於俄國手領土亦應收回 <br />\n<br />\n所以支共同俄佬咁friend 正正違反國安法"},{"pid":"9c2c4b1e70dbcff49160900708eadd9e458c0413","tid":2343851,"uid":119393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"所謂自古: <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e1/Han_Expansion.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fe%2Fe1%2FHan_Expansion.png&h=4e4fa7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日耳曼人公元前六世紀已經統治West Pomerania<br />\n比支那人侵略南越西甌駱越屠殺百越人早500年<br />\n夠晒資格話自古以來<br />\n二戰後都要吐返八九成出嚟<br />\n<br />\n以色列公元前六世紀亡國<br />\n1948年復國"},{"pid":"9a337a00ced78d09c5c71865ed9ed652fdbe874f","tid":2343851,"uid":33498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"南京自古是日本領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b173f2184fb0aa499d22cd1be770c7ecd4b4fc20","tid":2343851,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"所以呢個自古 其實係鳩up 任佢彈出又彈入"},{"pid":"4c621c90eecd0037